text.__SUMMARY__: Habenaria quinqueseta (longhorn bog orchid) is a species of  orchid closely related to H. macroceratitis and often mistaken for it.Habenaria quinqueseta is native to Central America, the West Indies (Cuba, the Bahamas, Hispaniola, Jamaica), southern Mexico (Oaxaca, Veracruz, Chiapas), northern South America (Colombia, Venezuela, the Guianas), and the southeastern United States (from Texas to South Carolina).
